issue.title: Minor refractoring (clean-up)
issue.body:
- renamed 'options' controller & routes (per request)
- added API values import from .env file
- minor refractoring 

With this update, server side will pull values from .env file (which needs to be present in project root directory)
**.env file example :**

DB_USER=<< put value here >>
DB_PASS=<< put pass here >>
DB=<< put db name here >>

DS_KEY=<< namara key >>
DS_ORG=<< namara org >>
